sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant UI as CLI or UI
  participant Store as SQLite KB Store
  participant AI as AI Package
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI API

  User->>UI: ask with Graph + Docs
  UI->>Store: searchEvidence(question, includeDocs=true)
  Store->>Store: keyword + symbol match graph nodes
  Store->>Store: find relevant repo/service/endpoint docs
  Store->>Store: prefer LLM doc, else deterministic doc
  Store-->>UI: evidence bundle with graph + docs
  UI->>AI: answerQuestion(evidence)
  alt OPENAI_API_KEY set
    AI->>OpenAI: send graph facts + selected generated docs
    OpenAI-->>AI: answer using graph as authority and docs as context
  else no key or API failure
    AI-->>UI: deterministic answer listing matched graph facts and docs used
  end
  UI-->>User: answer
